snippet.title: Cube Quest [Arcade Longplay] (1983) Simutrek
snippet.description: Full playthrough of the arcade game Cube Quest. Released back in 1983. Version from 01/04/84. First arcade game to feature 3D vector graphic. Also used are laserdisc overlay graphics. Played until 1,000,000 score is reached and 54 corridors are passed.
